Summary: Bus service in Brooklyn, the Bronx, Manhattan and Queens is running on a Saturday schedule
Description:
Bus service in Brooklyn, the Bronx, Manhattan and Queens is running on a Saturday schedule
If your bus does not normally operate on a Saturday, it will not run today.

Note: Staten Island bus service runs on a Sunday schedule

Summary: Southbound M1, M2, M3, and M55 stop on 5th Ave at W 38th is closed
Description:
Southbound M1, M2, M3, and M55 stop on 5th Ave at W 38th is closed
Please use the stops on 5th Ave at W 41st St or W 35th St.

What's happening?
Sidewalk construction

Summary: Southbound M1 and M1 LTD, M4 and M4 LTD and Westbound Q32 buses will not stop on 5th Ave at 49th St during the holiday season
Description:
Southbound M1 and M1 LTD, M4 and M4 LTD and Westbound Q32 buses will not stop on 5th Ave at 49th St during the holiday season
Use the stop on 5th Ave at 52nd St.

M1 and M4 local buses also stop on 5th Ave at 46 St.

Reminder: M1 LTD and M4 LTD buses do not run on weekends.
